From: Aurélien Hébert <aurelien.hebert@clever-cloud.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] base: Fix include
Upstream: no

Add <algorithm> to cover for std::max with initializer list.

GCC 14 requires explicit includes due to stricter C++20 compliance.
---
 src/base/discriminated-union.h | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/src/base/discriminated-union.h b/src/base/discriminated-union.h
--- a/src/base/discriminated-union.h
+++ b/src/base/discriminated-union.h
@@ -5,6 +5,7 @@
 #ifndef V8_BASE_DISCRIMINATED_UNION_H_
 #define V8_BASE_DISCRIMINATED_UNION_H_

+#include <algorithm>
 #include <type_traits>
 #include <utility>

